00:54:15.430 --> 00:54:19.450
what happens to the ones that are doing really
well and making progress in economic development

00:54:19.450 --> 00:54:20.800
-- merely on the commercial side?

00:54:20.800 --> 00:54:21.800
&gt;&gt;female #2: Um.

00:54:21.800 --> 00:54:25.920
&gt;&gt;Rahm Emanuel: So that's why, let's reform
the TIF's, let's get 'em on the budget, let's

00:54:25.920 --> 00:54:30.620
bring a level of transparency, let's set up
a standard for economic progress to measure

00:54:30.620 --> 00:54:36.470
before we offer a new mandate. And some are
already doing that and that doesn't mean that

00:54:36.470 --> 00:54:42.540
TIF's are the only way to achieve our goals
on affordable housing. Okay?

00:54:42.540 --> 00:54:43.540
